Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "But if Lyin’ Kamala Harris gets 4 more years, instead of a Golden Age, America will instead be plunged into a Dark Age. Your family finances will be permanently destroyed. Your borders will be gone forever."
